sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant JupyterWebApp as jupyter-web-app<br/>UI Frontend
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookReconciler as NotebookReconciler<br/>Controller
    participant StatefulSet as StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Instance
    participant NotebookPod as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant CullingReconciler as CullingReconciler<br/>Optional Controller
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collector
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,StatefulSet: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
        User->>JupyterWebApp: Request notebook creation
        JupyterWebApp->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: User credentials/SA token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookReconciler: Watch event (new Notebook CR)<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        NotebookReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        NotebookReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
        NotebookReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService (if USE_ISTIO=true)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
        K8sAPI->>StatefulSet: Schedule StatefulSet
        StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Launch Jupyter server
        NotebookPod-->>User: Notebook ready (via Istio VirtualService)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over CullingReconciler,NotebookReconciler: Flow 2: Notebook Culling (ENABLE_CULLING=true)
        CullingReconciler->>NotebookPod: GET /api/kernels<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None (or Istio mTLS)
        NotebookPod-->>CullingReconciler: Kernel activity response
        CullingReconciler->>CullingReconciler: Check idle time > CULL_IDLE_TIME
        CullingReconciler->>K8sAPI: Update Notebook CR<br/>Add STOP_ANNOTATION<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookReconciler: Watch event (Notebook updated)
        NotebookReconciler->>K8sAPI: Update StatefulSet (replicas=0)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI->>StatefulSet: Scale down to 0
        StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Terminate pod
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,NotebookReconciler: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>RBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: RBAC SubjectAccessReview
        RBACProxy->>RBACProxy: Verify permissions
        RBACProxy->>NotebookReconciler: Proxy to /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP localhost
        NotebookReconciler->>K8sAPI: List StatefulSets<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookReconciler: StatefulSet list
        NotebookReconciler->>NotebookReconciler: Calculate metrics<br/>(notebook_running, notebook_create_total, etc.)
        NotebookReconciler-->>RBACProxy: Metrics response
        RBACProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics (Prometheus format)
    end
